Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised because all of a sudden, you were collapsed on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I suddenly felt dizzy and tripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for making you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A slight anaemia, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? Do you want to go to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll get better if I rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Supplemental classes started already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't matter if you miss one class, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleep today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san, what about your part-time job?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take today off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to school with Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I played with Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A cicada flew into Yukito-san's breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.06,0:00:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the train station with Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the shrine with Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't read someone else's diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have anything else to write about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That diary is my masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to put it bluntly, you have no talent for keeping diaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So from now on, write about what you want to do, not what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's... not a diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's a diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make everything you write about come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go to the ocean with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.72,0:01:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,because I've never gone down to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to dig in the sand and pick up pretty shells.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We see the ocean all the time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Gao.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go the ocean together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That child said that she wanted to go to the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but I couldn't take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu collapsed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't recovered yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She's resting in her room right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll only get worse if I show her my alcohol-stenched face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget that; I bought sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a great time together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt me a LOT.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you take Misuzu in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you end up taking Misuzu in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she told you about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't take her in; she was pushed onto me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,though I said that I didn't want her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she isn't getting the love she needs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Realise it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only parent she has!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl has an attack when she becomes friends with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We distanced ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we can live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What is a parent-child relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a real parent, so I don't know very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuck, wrong sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,First, it's a dream of the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The dream gradually goes back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It starts to eat away at the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She begins to feel a pain that shouldn't be there, and gradually, the girl begins to forget everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She begins to forget even her most precious friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the morning after dreaming her last dream, the girl will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She is always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If she becomes close to another, both will become sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither of them will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So the girl said,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"Leave me."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a very kind and strong girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I was able to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But she...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In the sky, there is a girl with wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She is always alone and eventually disappears, unable to become an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She repeats such a sad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going on a trip?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'll drift around, travelling alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A hot springs tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do about Misuzu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving her in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't get too close to her, those attacks won't happen that easily, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu is dreaming right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That dream is making Misuzu behave like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered a story I heard from my mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum had met a girl with the same kind of sickness before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,After a while, Misuzu will begin to forget about me and about you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, after seeing her final dream, she'll probably die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there are some jokes that just can't be told.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you were awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I just woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Mummy's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she'll be out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I love Mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your time; don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I've walked this way many times, was the ocean always this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I... again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Those attacks again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll get better soon... so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the ocean... tomorrow, instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a dream again last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, it was a fun dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it was night-time, the sky was bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There was probably a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was watching from far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The person you're looking for and my dreams are connected, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They could be unrelated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you listen to the answer I found after much thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My dreams represent my other self,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and that girl is suffering right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try my best and dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,because I might be able to understand her that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do that, I might be able to save that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san, it's not by coincidence that I started seeing these dreams, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt that this year's summer was special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that I would do my best to make a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I met you and started seeing those dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably all connected, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want to try my hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make this summer the happiest because it's the summer that I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling better too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My feet won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be best to call Hijiri,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,or perhaps a big hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A doctor probably won't be able to heal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san, you understand too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My dreams are doing this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a dream last night too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream of travelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Travelling?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was travelling to find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked in the forest for days and days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It was hard, but I persevered,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,because a precious person was by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A precious person?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that as I dream, I gradually weaken until finally I... like the girl in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As if something like that could happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I got scolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to think about your other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just worry about recovering for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu-chin is a strong girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:12:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There can't be nothing wrong with a face like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My face was like this to start with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu, go back to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave you by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me worry about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with... this scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu, hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be better soon, so stay by my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I'm nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right; stay by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does everyone... leaving just me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to call Hijiri after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Or Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Minagi... is out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe someone from your class?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to cause them trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You want friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to be alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want you to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your being here is enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that trouble you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go to the ocean with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to play at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to race, throw water at each other, and when we're done, part saying, "See you tomorrow!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But for now, I'll hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, I'll be happier when I do go to the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu-chin, fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:13:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I plan on leaving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If I stay with you any longer, neither of us will live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've decided to run away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave this town and go to a place where I will never see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,By yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We've become... too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I really should have just played by myself like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This summer vacation that I spent with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no more buses?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, in my dream this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was locked up all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for a long time for someone to let me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I... want to go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,With you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any way for me to follow you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I want to leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to distance myself from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If I leave you, you should recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I can't stay by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for saying stupid things again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Byebye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're alone, hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try my best even if I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a strong girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you feeling now, Yukito?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel that you want the people who watch to laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's not the case, it won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The doll moves not just because of the wish to make it move but also because of the wish beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That child said, "I want to go to the ocean."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, finally, I want you to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside this doll, there are wishes that weren't granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother and my mother's mother, before losing their strength, sealed their powers inside this doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,For the eventual day when someone will release their wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I will become one of those wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It is up to you how you will use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can forget about the girl who lives in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Yukito...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In a town somewhere, you will probably meet a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to save her no matter what, put your heart into the doll,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,because I am with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Put my heart... in the doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's been weird like this for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's sick from the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to watch this and tell me how to make it more fun and how to make more people laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not that fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try doing more instead of just making it walk around?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it be part of a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it dance or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be more novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That performance was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun and cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for staying with me all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu, I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't go anywhere anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay with you and continue to make you laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned some tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They're definitely fun, so watch carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I notice until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just happy being by your side and seeing you smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If I just did that, I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't go anywhere anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Laugh by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you must remember now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...what you must do...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I want to be by Misuzu's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can, I would relive life from when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,with Misuzu... forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I couldn't get up anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You came back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm healthy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can try my hardest again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:23.38,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\c&H000000&\b1\pos(640,253)}SEIREKI: YEAR FIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch ouch ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You... Why are you in such a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have the leisure to open your mouth, please hurry and move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You're a face I'm not acquainted with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:36.64,Note,,0,0,0,,[Note: Lower Eighth Level]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shou Hachii Ge,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisakan of Saemon, Ryuuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And you... Where did you fall from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We just met.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly, I'm still somewhat unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The winged person I was ordered to protect is also named Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:21:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's truly a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When you say "winged person", you mean the gods' messengers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.77,0:23:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They are beings who can speak directly to the gods, can battle against famines and epidemics, and can purify and pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:23:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Family means to huddle together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.21,0:24:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I had never felt that being alone would be this painful.
